      • DataSource

        public DataSource(String name,
                  String description,
                  String type,
                  Long creationDate,
                  Long lastModifiedDate,
                  List<Permission> permissions,
                  org.bson.types.ObjectId owner,
                  String status,
                  String subtype,
                  String URL,
                  String username,
                  String password,
                  String resourceType,
                  String resource)
        Full constructor.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the datasource.
        description - the description of the datasource.
        type - the type of the datasource.
        creationDate - the creation date of the datasource.
        lastModifiedDate - the date of last update of the datasource.
        permissions - the permissions list of the datasource.
        owner - the owner of the datasource.
        status - the status of the datasource.
        subtype - the sub-type of the datasource.
        URL - the URL from which the datasource is accessible.
        username - the username to access the datasource.
        password - the password to access the datasource (for this current version of Metaware, this field is stored in plaintext).
        resourceType - the resource type in the datasource (can be: "table", "query", or "file").
        resource - the resource in the datasource (can be: "table name", "query", "file name").
